    <main>

      <div class="ians-column">

        <p>There are many different <strong>types of teams</strong> in the ATM environment and all of them are important. Some Teams have <strong>long-term</strong> working relationships (e.g. shift team) and some are <strong>passing</strong> (e.g. helpdesk staff and flight crew).</p>
        <p>In training there are also teams:</p>

